REFERENCE           JKOHTP
LANG_ENGLISH        "1) You must own Jedi Knight: Jedi Outcast.\n 2) Download the Movie Duels JKO addon file from ModDB and install it into your MD folder.\n 3) Go into your JKO GameData > base folder and rename the first 3 assets.pk3 files so they start with "0-".\n 4) Copy and paste the 3 renamed assets.pk3 files into your JKA base folder so it looks like the image below.\n\n You are now ready to start playing Jedi Outcast in MD."
LANG_CHINESE        "1) 您必须拥有绝地放逐者\n 2) 从 ModDB 下载 Movie Duels JKO 插件文件并将其安装到您的 MD 文件夹中。\n 3) 进入您的 JKO GameData > base 文件夹并重命名前 3 个。pk3 文件，使它们以“0-”开头。\n 4) 将 3 个重命名的 assets。pk3 文件复制并粘贴到您的 JKA 基本文件夹中，如下图所示.\n\n 您现在可以在退出电影决斗里玩绝地放逐者战役"

